5
One Move Captures Black (10)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to Play.\b0
\par At a glance, black appears to be alive.
\par
\par However, there is a move to capture black. It is a basic attacking method but it might be a blind spot for some.
\par
\par }
