Diagram 1 (Giving up)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Actually if you are 12K, it might be a little hard for you to solve this problem. If you are 10K, you might be able to solve it.
\par
\par If white acknowledges black to be alive, it is likely that white will play 1 in exchange for 2.
\par
\par White 3 is seonsu, but this is really only an endgame move.
\par }
