Diagram 3 (Mistake)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Ahha! It works to make placement at 1 and connect at 3! Well... some might think this so.
\par
\par However, this is mistaken.
\par Black 4 is a fantastic response and black lives. Now white can only play at 5, black plays dansu with 6 lives.
\par }
